15:44.318 --> 15:46.487
what Reese is capable of.

15:46.529 --> 15:48.239
I really don't think

15:46.529 --> 15:48.239
you do, because...

15:48.281 --> 15:51.451
Look, you may not want

15:48.281 --> 15:51.451
