16:21.063 --> 16:23.023
That guy's totally

16:21.063 --> 16:23.023
out to get you.

16:23.065 --> 16:25.318
Man! I was just using that

16:23.065 --> 16:25.318
as an excuse.

16:25.359 --> 16:27.737
He is so dead

16:25.359 --> 16:27.737
when Mom finds out!

16:27.779 --> 16:29.029
Reese, we can't bust him.

16:29.071 --> 16:31.031
If we rat him out,

16:29.071 --> 16:31.031
