16:35.995 --> 16:37.831
KIDS (chanting):

16:35.995 --> 16:37.831
Two is after one.

16:37.872 --> 16:40.750
Three is after two.

16:40.792 --> 16:43.336
Four is after three.

16:43.377 --> 16:48.716
Something is after something

16:48.758 --> 16:50.885
and then we get

16:48.758 --> 16:50.885
to ten!

