No, no, I-I'm just not going

17:07.109 --> 17:09.236
to do that, Francis.

17:09.278 --> 17:10.154
Hey, you

17:09.278 --> 17:10.154
guys better

17:10.196 --> 17:11.280
figure it out quick.

17:11.322 --> 17:13.240
This cheap-ass trash can's

17:11.322 --> 17:13.240
melting.

17:13.282 --> 17:15.075
Well, maybe you could

17:13.282 --> 17:15.075
talk to her then?

17:15.117 --> 17:17.328
Just calm her down

17:15.117 --> 17:17.328
so that I could come

17:15.117 --> 17:17.328
home, maybe today even?

17:17.370 --> 17:19.956
Francis, you've got to stop

17:17.370 --> 17:19.956
