So, fine, you win!

17:32.134 --> 17:33.093
Congratulations!

17:33.135 --> 17:34.595
This is your prize!

17:34.637 --> 17:36.723
Now, if you'll excuse me,

17:34.637 --> 17:36.723
I have to go.

17:36.764 --> 17:39.559
It smells like something died

17:36.764 --> 17:39.559
